legal.fanTerms.s8Body:
8.1  The Fan may not use the platform for unlawful purposes. In particular, it is prohibited to:
a)  provide false or misleading information during registration;
b)  use the platform for the purpose of harassment, stalking, or intimidation;
c)  upload content that is pornographic, glorifies violence, is racist, or is otherwise unlawful;
d)  distribute malware or malicious code through the platform;
e)  manipulate or disrupt the technical infrastructure of the platform.
8.2  In the event of violations, Fan Session is entitled to temporarily or permanently suspend the Fan Account.

legal.creatorTerms.s9Body:
9.1  The Creator may not use the platform for unlawful purposes. In particular, it is prohibited to:
a)  offer services outside the approved area of activity;
b)  offer illegal, dangerous, or morally objectionable services;
c)  provide false or misleading information in the profile or offering;
d)  use the platform to harass Fans;
e)  manipulate or disrupt the technical infrastructure of the platform;
f)  contact Fans outside the platform to circumvent payments.
9.2  In the event of violations, Fan Session is entitled to temporarily or permanently suspend the Creator Account and delete the Creator profile.
